[SHORT DESC]
Allows Seadra to evolve into Kingdra.

[LONG DESC]
<h2>Description</h2>
<p>Attach the Dragon Scale to Seadra and trade it to make it evolve into Kingdra. One-time use only. Raises the power of Dragon-type moves 10%. Found in Mt. Mortar and held by wild Horsea, Seadra, Dratini, and Dragonair (8%).</p>